Отличные новости!
Ко мне вернулось обоняние 🥰
Радуюсь как ребёнок каждому запаху 😍
Неделю я вообще не ощущала своим носом ничего! Такое себе ощущение, когда вся еда имеет одинаковый привкус, а подаренные цветы не могут порадовать своим ароматом. Зато сейчас я снова открываю арома-мир и это счастье глубоко дышать и ощущать мир на вкус ☺️
Доктор, которая посещала меня в прошлое воскресенье, сказала, что когда вернётся обоняние, значит я почти выздоровела 😇
Кстати - завтра заканчивается мой курс лечения, а из поликлиники больше никто не приходил и не звонил. Интересно, когда к пациенту придут в следующий раз 🤔
И ещё из новостей - говорят в лабораториях очень увеличилось количество желающих сдать тесты ПЦР. Может сказывается, что люди возвращаются из отпусков перед началом учебного года, а может это начало второй волны... 
Берегите себя 🙏🏻

#covid #covid19 #коронавирус #танцующийэкономист #ячувствуюмир

node.text:
Самый мощный суперкомпьютер проанализировал, какой тип маски лучше всего защищает от коронавируса.

Суперкомпьютер Fugaku, названный самым мощным в мире, уже давно работает над изобретением препарата COVID-19. С его помощью также удалось провести симуляцию, указывающую на то, какой тип масок лучше всего защищает от выхода вирусов и бактерий из носа и рта. И достаточно сказать, что результат для многих может быть неожиданным.

С помощью японского суперкомпьютера Fugaku была проведена симуляция защиты от выхода выделений из горла (например, при кашле) на основе трех видов масок – нетканых (одноразовых из полипропилена), хлопчатобумажных и полиэфирных.

Моделирование, проведенное компанией Riken, показало, что микробы лучше всего блокируют обычные нетканые одноразовые маски, доступные во многих магазинах и используемые в азиатских странах во время сезона гриппа. Хлопок и полиэстер, также защищают, но только с 80-процентной эффективностью. Нетканые маски из полиприлена блокировали почти все молекулы во время имитируемого кашля.

Интересно, что "хирургическая" версия масок оказалась несколько менее эффективной и пропускала ок. 10% микробов размером 20 микрометров (1 микрометр = 1/1 000 000 метров) или меньше. Такие маски, согласно симуляции, выпускают микробы через щели между краем маски и нашим лицом. Маски из полиэстера и хлопка выпускали до 40% меньших частиц.

Нередко мы встречаемся на улицах с самодельными масками, но оказывается, что недоверие к одноразовым, доступным во многих магазинах, не совсем оправдано. Несмотря на тонкий слой, их конструкция и материал, из которого они сделаны, также достаточно эффективны для блокирования молекул, вылетающих во время кашля.

node.text:
Last week marked a devastating loss to the global education community. Sir Ken Robinson, the renowned education reformer, passed away. 

He was an extraordinary educationalist whose commitment and passion for bringing about change in the education system was remarkable.

His vision through his work, various articles, books and the renowned TED Talk inspired not only people in the education world over but also us inside SOAL.

His vision of embracing creativity & changing the hierarchy of subjects taught in school, valuing failure & opting for modern methods of teaching have all become a part of our value system at SOAL.

His work was transformational for both students & teachers alike. #RIP

node.text:
🇭🇺BELÜLRŐL JÖN, MÉGIS MÁSTÓL VÁRJUK 🤔
✋Ahogy már 3000 éve Buddha is megmondta, a békét önmagadban keresd, ne a külvilágban.

🎃Azaz, volt már olyan hogy azt vártad majd békésebb leszel ha nem lesz #covid, bevándorlás, problémás főnök, ha elérted az összes célod, megvetted az álom autód, milliomos lettél vagy a külvilágtól vártad hogy megnyugodsz? 

🌻Vannak olyan dolgok amik nem rajtunk múlnak és van olyan ami igen. Amit elérsz, megkapsz, megoldasz természetesen hoz egyfajta megnyugvást és boldogságot de ez rövid életű és instabil. Hamar jön a következő vágy, probléma, határidő. Az elme nincs hozzászokva, trénelve ehhez az állapothoz. 

👾A meditáció viszont egy eszköz arra hogy a belső megnyugvást, békét Te magad érd el, mindenféle külső hatástól függetlenül.

😎Tetszene ha mindig békés, boldog lehetnél? Akkor itt az idő hogy kipróbáld a meditációt. Ebben tudok segíteni csak írj rám ;) Vagy nézd meg a különböző lehetőségeket a bioban is. 

💫💫💫💫💫💫💫💫💫💫💫

🇬🇧COMING FROM INSIDE, YET WE ARE WAITING FROM OUTSIDE 🤔
✋As the Buddha said 3,000 years ago, seek peace in yourself, not outside. 

🎃Did happen to you that you expected to be more peaceful if there is no #covid, immigration, problematic boss, if you achieved all your goals, bought your dream car, became a millionaire, or did you expect the outside world to give you a reason to be peaceful?

🌻There are things that do not depend on us and there are things that do. What you achieve, you get, you solve, of course it brings a kind of reassurance and happiness but it is short-lived and unstable. Soon comes the next desire, problem, deadline. The mind is not trained to keep this peaceful state.

👾Meditation, is a tool to achieve inner calm and peace, regardless of any external influences.

😎Would you like to be always peaceful and happy? Then it's time to try meditation. I can help with this just write to me;) Or look at the different options in the bio as well.

Ja tinc la imatge d'aquest estiu. La imatge és bonica, però l'estiu per mi, no ha estat bonic.

Però aquest agost, sí ha tingut de bonic sentir la fortalesa de la companyia de la nit estrellada, aquesta part del que sóc, passejant per Prada. Pare, mare.

He sentit de nou l'enyor que sembla haver-se impregnat per sempre en els meus estius sense ells. Ells i elles, com em falten.

He sentit la tristor de la pèrdua, de tantes pèrdues aquesta primavera que m'han culpit aquest estiu.

He sentit la ràbia del desconcert, del camí difuminat. He sentit nostàlgia, tristor, impotència...

I no em fa res compartir-ho aquí, perquè no, per mi la vida compartida és millor. 

Però malgrat tot aquest agost, aquí tinc la imatge del meu estiu fet bonic perquè amb ell he trobat l'anclatge davant l'abisme i perquè amb ell, sumem quatre.

#estiu2020 #covid-19

Indian cuisine consists of a variety of regional and traditional cuisines native to the Indian subcontinent. Given the diversity in soil, climate, culture, ethnic groups, and occupations, these cuisines vary substantially and use locally available spices, herbs, vegetables, and fruits. Indian food is also heavily influenced by religion, in particular Hinduism, cultural choices and traditions.Centuries of Islamic rule, particularly by the Mughals, also introduced dishes like samosa and pilaf.

node.text:
En tiempos de #COVID homenajeamos la “Festa Major de Vilafranca del Penedès”
.
En medio del REPIQUE GENERAL DE CAMPANAS Y FORTÍSIMA TRONADA, hay nervios, todo el mundo está ansioso por el comienzo de la "Festa Major" un tiempo mágico lleno de emoción, la carne de gallina indica que una vez más ya está aquí la "Festa"
.
Las calles se llenan para acompañar los espectáculos de música, fuego y bailes que marca la entrada del Santo en la Basílica de Santa María. Bailes en las calles, teatro, conciertos y atracciones completan una fiesta que tiene en la participación popular su elemento clave.
.

.

С детства я почему-то очень запомнила фильм "Лангольеры", как было страшно, но сквозь окутывающую тревогу и страх я все равно смотрела этот фильм. И вот 2020 год будто ремейк этого фильма о том, как миллионы страшных зубастых монстров перемалывают своими острыми зубами оставшиеся кусочки привычной реальности..вне логики, вне разума, будто мы действительно попали в какое-то неведомое четвёртое измерение, но всё еще не понимаем, как избежать окончательной катастрофы..и вынуждены просто смотреть этот фильм🎬, будучи не в силах что-либо сделать. Остаётся только пытаться эпизодично отгонять тревогу и надеяться, что мы уже скоро увидим финальные кадры, когда нормальное настоящее снова догонит вот это непонятно что..

node.text:
✊ 💜 Activistas feministas que trabajan en la intersección entre la justicia de género y la justicia climática.
​
​1) Majandra Rodriguez Acha - @majandraa, activista de justicia de género.
​"No somos máquinas, ¿sabes? Estamos intentando de construir un nuevo sistema, así que tenemos que actuar en consecuencia. Si nos comprometemos con los y las demás y trabajamos conjuntamente en nuestro bienestar colectivo e individual, en nuestra humanidad compartida, solo así podremos construir un futuro mejor aquí y ahora." 
​
​​​@fridafund
​@tierractivaperu
​@wedo_worldwide
​@globalgreengrants
​
​2) Meera Ghani, activista feminista de Pakistán.
"​Los valores están en el epicentro de todo. Si queremos alejarnos de los sistemas de la violencia, tenemos que reimaginar un mundo que se centre en los valores. Hemos interiorizado el capitalismo como la forma en que definimos nuestra propia valía. La cultura de los valores es radicalmente opuesta a todo esto. Se trata de la abundancia que existe entre los seres humanos y la naturaleza. Entrelazarlos, interconectarnos, ser interdependientes." 

​ @theeggisyou @moxie.cc
​
​Ilustraciones:@maanya_dhar
​
​Para descubrir más sobre ellas y otras feministas, descargue su copia gratuita de Clima, covid y valores: Trayectorias feministas aquí: 👉oxf.am/trayectoriasfeministas o en el enlace de nuestras stories 👆

𝟐𝟕 𝐇𝐞𝐚𝐥𝐭𝐡 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐍𝐮𝐭𝐫𝐢𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐓𝐢𝐩𝐬 𝐓𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐀𝐫𝐞 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐮𝐚𝐥𝐥𝐲 𝐄𝐯𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞-𝐁𝐚𝐬𝐞𝐝
(PART 1)
◻️𝟭. 𝗗𝗼𝗻’𝘁 𝗱𝗿𝗶𝗻𝗸 𝘀𝘂𝗴𝗮𝗿 𝗰𝗮𝗹𝗼𝗿𝗶𝗲𝘀
Sugary drinks are among the most fattening items you can put into your body. Sugary drinks are strongly associated with obesity, type 2 diabetes, heart disease, and many other health problems
◻️𝟮. 𝗘𝗮𝘁 𝗻𝘂𝘁𝘀
Despite being high in fat, nuts are incredibly nutritious and healthy. Studies demonstrate that nuts can help you lose weight and may help fight type 2 diabetes and heart disease. Additionally, your body doesn’t absorb 10–15% of the calories in nuts. Some evidence also suggests that this food can boost metabolism
◻️𝟯. 𝗔𝘃𝗼𝗶𝗱 𝗽𝗿𝗼𝗰𝗲𝘀𝘀𝗲𝗱 𝗷𝘂𝗻𝗸 𝗳𝗼𝗼𝗱
Processed junk food is incredibly unhealthy.
They’re usually low in fiber, protein, and micronutrients but high in unhealthy ingredients like added sugar and refined grains. Thus, they provide mostly empty calories
◻️𝟰. 𝗗𝗼𝗻’𝘁 𝗳𝗲𝗮𝗿 𝗰𝗼𝗳𝗳𝗲𝗲
Coffee is very healthy.
It’s high in antioxidants, and studies have linked coffee intake to longevity and a reduced risk of type 2 diabetes, Parkinson’s and Alzheimer’s diseases, and numerous other illnesses 
◻️𝟱. 𝗘𝗮𝘁 𝗳𝗮𝘁𝘁𝘆 𝗳𝗶𝘀𝗵
Fish is a great source of high-quality protein and healthy fat. This is particularly true of fatty fish, such as salmon, which is loaded with omega-3 fatty acids and various other nutrients.  Studies show that people who eat the most fish have a lower risk of several conditions, including heart disease, dementia, and depression
◻️𝟲. 𝗚𝗲𝘁 𝗲𝗻𝗼𝘂𝗴𝗵 𝘀𝗹𝗲𝗲𝗽
The importance of getting enough quality sleep cannot be overstated. Poor sleep can drive insulin resistance, disrupt your appetite hormones, and reduce your physical and mental performance

😷Le préfet rend le port du masque obligatoire dans les 22 communes de la métropole d'Orléans

Cette mesure s'applique du samedi 29/08/20 à 8h jusqu'au mercredi 30/09/20 minuit.

En concertation avec le directeur général de l'Agence régionale de Santé et le président de la métropole d'Orléans, le préfet du Loiret a pris ce jour un arrêté rendant le port du masque obligatoire pour les personnes de plus de 11 ans dans l'espace public ou dans un lieu ouvert au public, sur l'ensemble du territoire des 22 communes de la métropole d'Orléans.
Boigny-sur-Bionne, Bou, Chanteau, La Chapelle-St-Mesmin, Chécy, Combleux, Fleury-les-Aubrais, Ingré, Mardié, Marigny-les-Usages, Olivet, Orléans, Ormes, Saint-Cyr en-Val, Saint-Denis-en-Val, Saint-Hilaire-Saint-Mesmin, Saint-Jean-de-Braye, Saint-Jean-La-Ruelle, Saint-Jean-le-Blanc, Saint-Pryvé-St-Mesmin, Saran, Semoy.

Sont concernés, les piétons, joggers, cyclistes, utilisateurs de trottinette ou de gyropod, etc...

Plusieurs facteurs justifient cette mesure :
➡️ la dégradation de la situation épidémique dans le département depuis plusieurs semaines et le caractère actif de la propagation du virusdémontre une augmentation du nombre de tests positifs de 70% au cours des deux dernières semaines.
➡️ le taux d'incidence est de 52,7%/100 000 habitants, supérieur au seuil d'alertede50/100 000. Ce taux était de 6, 9/100 000 au début du mois d'août. Il est actuellement trois fois supérieur au premier seuil de vigilance retenu par Santé Publique France.
➡️ le taux de positivité des tests réalisés est désormais de 4% contre 0,86% à la mi-juillet.
➡️ la circulation active du virus est principalement concentrée sur la métropole d'Orléans.

Le non-respect de cette obligation expose les contrevenants à une amende de 135 €.

source : www.loiret.gouv.fr/Actualites/Le-prefet-rend-le-port-du-masque-obligatoire-dans-les-22-communes-de-la-metropole-d-Orleans

node.text:
W e e k  s e v e n t y  s i x

This week we had a home visit from a Leckey rep and Elliot’s physio to trial a new stander.  The Monkey stander we currently have is great but Elliot needs support behind his head for when he becomes uncomfortable or tired as his extension kicks in and he throws his head back with force - we have now found something more suitable so that, plus a walker, is now on order!

🖤

It was great for the physio to see and feel how Elliot has progressed in the last 6 months, she was impressed.  It now means that if we go back to online appointments because of a Covid spike then she has felt his current tone and movement and can develop a further programme for him. He made it known that he didn’t want to do anymore and signed finish to her 😂

🖤

I’ve been a bit of a mix bag of emotions this week and really feeling the pressure of Ethan going back to school.  I cant seem to switch off from it, I’m sure every parent is feeling anxieties to an extent, it is so consuming. The past 6 months have had a noticeable impact on Ethan mentally, which we have been trying to manage, but I am hoping that a dose of school (albeit far from normal) will help him. He needs his friends, he needs some school structure back and he needs reassurance that it will be ok.  Please be ok.

🖤

Stay safe

🖤

Azzardo...potrebbe essere che isolamento e distanza sociale non sono proprio fatti per il nostro cervello...?!
@thepatrizio credo che oltre all'isolamento e alla distanza sociale, il nostro cervello sia messo a dura prova da eventi come l'emergenza sanitaria che abbiamo vissuto.
@thepatrizio eventi stressanti, destabilizzanti dunque potenzialmente traumatizzanti.

➡️"Secondo uno studio condotto dal San Raffaele di Milano, oltre la metà delle persone che hanno ricevuto una qualche forma di trattamento ospedaliero per #CoViD-19 riporta almeno un #sintomo di disturbi come #ansia, #depressione, #stress #post-traumatico, #insonnia o altre manifestazioni. La storia personale di ciascuno, la durata del ricovero e anche il genere del paziente influiscono sull'entità di questi #strascichi, che vanno trattati prima che possano degenerare in condizioni croniche fortemente debilitanti.
↘️All'origine dei disturbi potrebbero esserci gli stati infiammatori associati alla #malattia e legati alla risposta immunitaria dell'#organismo. È noto infatti che gli stati infiammatori, anche conseguenti a infezioni virali, sono fattori di rischio per disturbi come la depressione. Ma un impatto importante potrebbero averlo avuto anche #fattorisociali, come lo #stresspsicologico associato a una condizione sconosciuta e potenzialmente letale, l'#isolamento forzato da parenti e personale medico, la #paura di trasmettere il #virus ad altri, il #pregiudizio che purtroppo sempre ruota attorno a chi è #malato"

node.text:
#whataboutweddings 

At the beginning of this year @theweddingarrangers had 38 weddings in the diary. We managed to complete just one of those. Thankfully out of the rest only 3 have actually cancelled whilst the rest have postponed. At every event we employ waiters, chefs, bar tenders, lighting engineers, bands, djs, photographers, florists, hire companies, sound engineers, security, waste collectors.... What a hit to the economy this is. Without even mentioning the emotional impact on our couples.

To be clear, The Wedding Arrangers are NOT asking to run events until it is safe to do so. We want your granny there as much as you do. But if we are not able to go back to work we need ongoing financial support from the government. A sector specific approach is sorely lacking. The Wedding Arrangers stand by all hospitality and events professionals in this.

I had so many educational insta post idea plans this past week and I ended up posting none. 

I was asked if I was ok after our Friday Zoom training as I seemed a bit flat and yes, I was bit flat.

I have been asked if I am ok and I am probably not ok. I feel...I am actually not sure what I feel to be honest.

I have great support in my family. 

I am still able to do my own training and I enjoy it. 

My Zoom training team is bunch of positive people and we have so much fun. 

We have an amazing neighborhood here where I live and I couldn’t be more grateful for that.

So no. I have no reason to complain and feel flat. My life is far from hard or complicated. 

But I guess “this” whatever is happening in Victoria now, has been going on for bit too long now and I cannot see the end of it.

I don’t have any moral to this post. Just if you feel the same you are definitely not alone. 

My friend pretty much summed it up for me when she said: “I feel you, it’s just the same s*** every day”.

So yeah, I don’t feel alone, I got my family and you guys, but it still isn’t easy!!!

Do you know your COVID-19 status? It's so easy, fast and cheap to know.

If you're in or around Plateau state, we have documented 9 key points from our weekly radio programme #OOTCPlateau on KT 103.9 FM yesterday that you need to know about COVID-19 testing in order to stay safe: 

1. That without testing it is impossible to tell who is positive for the virus and who is not. You can’t also tell who should be isolated or quarantined, who should be discharged from the isolation centre or who should remain.

2. That Plateau state has tested 23,000 persons so far for COVID-19 and comparing this figure with the population of Plateau state which is estimated around 3.5million, we haven't tested 1% of the population yet. Testing centres need to run in full capacity and in other to increase the number of  tests carried out per day.

3. The NCDC approved testing centres in Plateau state include; NVRI Vom, Plateau Specialist Hospital, Jos University Teaching Hospital JUTH. Any other centre testing for COVID-19 in state is unapproved and illegal in nature.

4. That COVID-19 testing is absolutely free and done at no cost! 

5. That the rise in positive cases in the state is not solely dependent on the slight scale-up of the testing in the state. It only indicates that more people have been infected which is clearly seen through the increase in community transmission of the virus. This places a lot of emphasis on the need for citizens to abide by all the safety guidelines provided against COVID-19.

node.text:
Studies suggest this and not me🤷🤷. Can't argue with science right?. Well history has always shown how women are also equipped to lead. Far from the "weaker vessel" image that people portray us to act like, it's been proven that women also have leader like skills and knowledge to expand and build. From the littlest group (the home) to the biggest continent, Women, once they put their kind to it, can lead and be successful. However in India, Women aren't significantly valued in politics.

Women turnout during India's parliamentary general elections was 65.63%, compared to 67.09% turnout for men. India ranks 20th from the bottom in terms of representation of women in Parliament. Women have held the posts of president and prime minister in India, as well as chief ministers of various states. Indian voters have elected women to numerous state legislative assemblies and national ministry for many decades We, however hope that one day, Women politicians will have a significant number.

The Hon'ble Supreme Court dismissed a petition seeking directions to refrain from holding the upcoming elections in Bihar till the state is declared COVID-19 and flood-free.

The Hon'ble court said that Covid19 cannot be a ground for postponement of elections, especially when the notification declaring the election has not even been issued.

The Hon'ble SC further said that the Election Commission will take all precautionary steps to ensure the safety of the citizens.

#ClassInforma #29Ago  #Bolivia flexibilizará la cuarentena después de cinco meses ante la necesidad de recuperar la economía, para evitar que del coronavirus se pase al «coronahambre», aseveró este viernes la presidenta interina del país, Jeanine Añez.

«La gente necesita salir a trabajar», sentenció Añez ante los periodistas durante un acto en La Paz.

La mandataria transitoria se refirió en estos términos a la decisión de que a partir de septiembre el país pase de la cuarentena decretada en marzo por la COVID-19 a lo que denomina una fase de «posconfinamiento», con menos restricciones a fin de que se recupere la economía después de cinco meses.

La presidenta interina subrayó que «la gente tiene la necesidad de trabajar, porque si no es por el coronavirus, es por el coronahambre (…), uno se desespera cuando no tiene las condiciones económicas para llevar alimento a casa, preocupa no tener la platita para llevar a la casa».

Jeanine Añez defendió la necesidad de «abrir la economía», confiando en que no haya un rebrote de la enfermedad en el país, aunque en otros casos no han podido evitarlo ni potencias mundiales con más recursos.

Los fallecidos en el país por #COVID-19 son 4.791 y 113.129 los casos confirmados, aunque en los últimos días el reporte de positivos ha llegado a bajar de los 1.000 diarios mientras que en jornadas anteriores superaba ligeramente los 2.000, según datos oficiales.

Vía : EFE

node.text:
Il rientro a scuola si avvicina e tante sono le incognite che accompagnano questo momento.
Anche in un anno "normale" e senza Covid, però, il momento è delicato e i primi giorni di scuola sono sempre un rito di passaggio sia per i genitori che, soprattutto, per i figli.
Io ho provato a raccontare con ironia, sorriso e un pizzico di irriverenza l'ansia, le aspettative, i mal di pancia e anche la voglia di tornare tra i banchi.
E voi? Come avete vissuto il vostro primo giorno di scuola da bambini? E da genitori? 
Perché la scuola la si fa sempre due volte: una da protagonisti e l'altra da tifosi del successo dei propri figli.

#COVID-19 AND #WOMENFARMERS

Women farmers are typically engaged in #multiplelivelihoods as #cultivators #wagelabourers livestock readers #collectorsofforestproduce in #fisheries etc. But their work, their contribution and their very identity as #farmers continue to go #unrecorded and #unacknowledged Their identity as a ‘farmer’ continues to evoke the #standardimageofaman Women farmers rarely have #accesstoland and consequently #noaccesstocredit and are excluded from #decisionmaking over #naturalresources such as #water . The #State #communities and #families are responsible for this #structuralexclusion of women farmers from accessing their #rights over their #ownlabour and produce. At this moment of #Pandemic #Women who are the producers and providers of our #basicneeds are deprived of

node.text:
When the party is cancelled, we celebrate anyway!⁣
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⁣
It was last October when Kris & Louise met with me and we were talking about their ideal wedding plans for their August 2020 wedding. Little did we know what 2020 had in store for all of us.⁣
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⁣
Kris & Louise made the decision a few months ago at the height of Covid, to push their wedding back to next year, and it wasn’t a decision that was made lightly. I knew that their original wedding date of 22nd August 2020 would be an emotional one, knowing that they would have been getting married last Saturday, had everything gone ahead as planned. So to switch things up, and create some happiness in each of our lives (this was a joy for me too!) I reached out and we organised a photoshoot to celebrate their original wedding date.⁣
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⁣
And it was so worth it.⁣
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⁣
It was so nice to be back shooting again and this image was a fun little experiment 😍

The National Sports Awards is being conducted virtually on 29 August for the first time in history due to Covid-19, with 65 awardees are expected to attend the ceremony via online. 
⬇️⬇️
The awards will be conferred by the Hon'ble President of India Ram Nath Kovind virtually and will be launched at 11 AM on 29 August 2020. 
⬇️⬇️
On this National Sports Day, unlike other years awardees would not make the customary walk on the red carpet inside Rashtrapati Bhawan's Durbar Hall, but the national sports awards will be held at chosen 76 Sports Authority of India (SAI) centre and other venues closest to them from, where they will be connected to the President at his residence, through Doordarshan's camera crews. 
⬇️⬇️
The award ceremony is being held simultaneously across Bengaluru, Pune, Sonepat, Chandigarh, Kolkata, Lucknow, Delhi, Mumbai, Bhopal, Hyderabad and Itanagar.
⬇️⬇️
The event will be telecast live on Doordarshan and streamed live on https://webcast.gov.in/myas/sportsawards/.
⬇️⬇️
The National Sports Awards is underway with Honourable President Ram Nath Kovind.
⬇️⬇️
The Sports Minister Kiren Rijiju says that this is the first award ceremony to be held in the time of coronavirus pandemic in India.

node.text:
Black Panther star, Chadwick Boseman, dies of cancer

Hollywood actor, Chadwick Boseman, best known for his stunning role in Marvel’s blockbuster superhero movie, “Black Panther” is dead.
The 43-year-old actor passed away in his Los Angeles home with his wife, Taylor Ledward, and other family members by his side, after battling a chronic colon cancer for four years, a statement by his family said on Friday night.
“A true fighter, Chadwick persevered through it all and brought you many of the films you have come to love so much,” his family said in the statement posted on Twitter.
The statement said he was diagnosed with stage three colon cancer in 2016, and that the disease progressed ultimately to stage four.
Until his death, Boseman never spoke publicly about his health problem. His family said he was always under the knife during most of his filming projects.
“From Marshall to Da 5 Bloods, August Wilson’s Ma Rainey’s Black Bottom and several more — all were filmed during and between countless surgeries and chemotherapy. It was the honor of his career to bring King T’Challa to life in Black Panther,” the statement read.

node.text:
Ganja resmi menjadi tanaman binaan Kementerian Pertanian (Kementan). Tanaman dengan bahasa latin cannabis sativa itu masuk ke dalam kategori komoditas tanaman obat.

Menteri Pertanian Syahrul Yasin Limpo menetapkan hal tersebut melalui Surat Keputusan Menteri Pertanian RI Nomor 184/KPTS/HK.140/M/2/2020 tentang Komoditas Binaan Kementerian Pertanian. Ia menandatangani keputusan tersebut pada 3 Februari 2020.

"Menetapkan keputusan menteri pertanian tentang komoditas binaan Kementerian Pertanian," demikian tertulis dalam surat yang dikutip Suara.com, Sabtu (29/8/2020).

Komoditas binaan Kementerian Pertanian meliputi komoditas binaan Direktorat Jenderal yakni tanaman pangan, holtikultura, perkebunan, peternakan dan kesehatan hewan.

Surat keputusan itu juga sekaligus menggantikan Keputusan Menteri Pertanian Nomor 141/Kpts/HK.150/M/2/2019 tentang Jenis Komoditas Tanaman Binaan Lingkup Kementerian Pertanian yang sudah diterbitkan sebelumnya.

node.text:
Salamah Damanik (60), warga Huta II, Nagori Lias Baru, Kecamatan Bandar Masilam, Kabupaten Simalungun, ditemukan tidak bernyawa, dalam kondisi tergantung.

AKP Lukman Hakim, Kasubbag Humas Polres Simalungun, kepada wartawan, pada Jumat (28/8/2020) lalu, pukul 09.00 WIB menjelaskan, Polsek Perdagangan menerima informasi dari masyarakat tentang adanya orang meninggal.

Menurut keterangan saksi, di TKP, Nurmala Purba (34), tetangga korban, yang biasa mengantar sarapan untuk korban,  dia melihat jendela dan pintu rumah korban masih dalam keadaan tertutup dan terkunci, sehingga saksi memanggil-manggil korban, namun tidak disahut.

Selanjutnya saksi memanggil dan mengajak teman-temannya, yaitu Ernawati Tamba dan Yulinar. Mereka bersama-sama ke belakang rumah korban dan mencungkil dinding dapur yang terbuat dari tepas.

Saksi dan teman-temannya, langsung masuk ke dalam rumah dan kaget bukan main saat melihat korban tergantung dengan leher terjerat tali nilon, pada tiang atau pilar rumah.

Menurut tenaga medis, yaitu Evi Novelia Damanik, S.Km, Kepala Puskesmas Bandar Tinggi dan Bidan Rosena Purba, tidak ditemukan bekas atau tanda – tanda kekerasan (tindak pidana) pada tubuh korban.

#LangLangKota MayangkaraNews.com ► Hasil rapid tes 130 Petugas Badan Pusat Statistik Kota Blitar, sebelum melakukan sensus penduduk dari rumah ke rumah pada september mendatang, dinyatakan non -reaktif.

Kepala Badan Pusat Statistik Kota Blitar Erny Fatma Setyoharini mengatakan, dari 130 petugas BPS yang mengikuti rapid tes, sebelum melakukan sensus penduduk dari rumah ke rumah, hasilnya semua dinyatakan non-reaktif. 130 petugas itu terdiri dari 102 petugas sensus , 9 koordinasi sensus kecamatan dan 19 orang staff BPS Kota Blitar. Erny menjelaskan, sebelumnya 24-27 Agustus lalu, BPS Kota Blitar menggelar rapid tes sebagai bentuk seleksi petugas sensus di tengah pandemi #Covid-19 ini. 

Selain itu untuk memastikan kondisi petugas sebelum terjun kelapangan dari rumah ke rumah. Sehingga bisa dipastikan, semua petugas sensus penduduk yang  turun ke lapangan, mendata dari rumah ke rumah dalam keadaan sehat. Erny mengatakan, pihaknya meminta kepada masyarakat tidak perlu khawatir dan takut saat menerima petugas sensus, sebab petugas juga memakai alat pelindung diri, seperti memakai masker, face shild, sarung tangan dan membawa handsinitizer, serta menjaga jarak saat proses sensus berlangsung.

Erny menambahkan, sensus penduduk akan dimulai pada 1 September 2020. [Nindy]

Покатал девочек гонщик👍глаза из задницы забыл достать...

«Mercedes в клочья, реанимация перевернулась». В ночной аварии в центре Перми пострадали три человека.

Ночные покатушки в очередной раз обернулись жесткой аварией на Октябрьской площади, - написала в соцсетях очевидец ночного ДТП, произошедшего на Октябрьской площади. - Перевернутая реанимация с мигалками, к ней со всех сторон несутся люди. Звонок пожарным и в «скорую». Первыми приехали пожарные, затем одна за другой «скорые», спасатели. В реанимации пациента не было, но водитель и бригада явно пострадали. Но как же кричала женщина... До сих пор этот крик боли и страха стоит в ушах...
Страшное ДТП, в котором пострадали три человека, произошло ночью на субботу, 29 августа, на Октябрьской площади в Перми.

Столкновение произошло в 2.16 ночи, - сообщил «КП»-Пермь» источник в правоохранительных органах. - В районе дома №96 по улице Екатерининская столкнулись карета реанимобиля и автомобиль Mercedes. В результате удара карета «скорой медицинской помощи» опрокинулась на бок.

В результате аварии пострадали 38-летний водитель легкового автомобиля и две его пассажирки – обеим женщинам по 30 лет. Они получили травмы различной степени тяжести и все трое были госпитализированы в пермскую краевую клиническую больницу. В карете «скорой помощи», к счастью, пострадавших нет.
Сейчас по факту ДТП проводится проверка. Выясняются причины, которые привели к столкновению транспортных средств. Есть очевидцы, которые высказывают в соцсетях мнение, что это иномарка подрезала реанимобиль, поэтому и произошла эта авария.

Mungkin sebagian dari kita masih bertanya-tanya, saat menyaksikan pertandingan sepakbola di televisi, kita sering kali melihat pemain sepakbola minum air dari botol tetapi kemudian meludahkannya kembali.

Dan ternyata, menurut para ilmuwan nutrisi yang dikutip oleh New York Times . Itu adalah trik untuk menipu otak agar mendapatkan rangsangan pada otot yang kelelahan.

Ketika air memenuhi mulut, maka yang terjadi adalah reseptor mulut dirangsang mendeteksi beberapa jenis karbohidrat dan mengirim sinyal "kegembiraan" ke pusat-pusat kesenangan otak.

Persepsinya adalah akan ada lebih banyak energi dalam meredakan stres dan membuat otot bekerja lebih banyak tanpa melelahkan atlet.

Dan semakin lama cairan berada di dalam mulut, semakin besar kontak dengan reseptor oral dan semakin baik hasilnya. Jangan menelannya, karena itu akan mempengaruhi kinerja dengan gangguan pencernaan.

Nah. Itulah kenapa para pemain sepakbola terlihat sering meludahkan kembali saat mereka minum, mereka hanya membilas mulut untuk memanipulasi otak, tidak meminumnya, karena bisa mempengaruhi kinerja.

Personel Unit Reskrim Polsek Patumbak menggagalkan peredaran 10 kg sabu di Kota Medan. Dalam pengungkapan ini, petugas mengamankan dua orang tersangka di dua lokasi berbeda.

Kapolsek Patumbak, Kompol Arfin Fachreza mengatakan penangkapan pelaku pada Minggu (23/8/2020) itu berawal dari pengungkapan kasus 4 kg sabu yang dilakukan Polsek Patumbak pada Selasa (14/7/2020) lalu. Dalam pengungkapan tersebut, petugas menangkap tersangka Aswandi dan kawan-kawan.

“Dari penangkapan tersebut kita mendapat informasi akan ada pengiriman narkoba kembali," kata Arfin, Jumat (28/8/2020).

Berbekal informasi tersebut, petugas mengamankan tersangka Basri alias Bas saat melintas di Jalan Megawati, Kota Binjai, Sabtu (22/8/2020). Dalam penangkapan tersebut, petugas mengamankan barang bukti 10 kemasan teh China berisi sabu seberat 10 kg dalam satu goni besar.

“Dari pemeriksaan, tersangka bas mengaku jika narkoba tersebut akan diedarkan di kawasan Langkat dan dikendalikan oleh Muhamad Basri alias Brewok. Selanjutnya kita lakukan pengembangan dan amankan Brewok di salah satu diskotik,” ungkap Arfin.

node.text:
NEW BLOG POST
....
Remember cutting up folded bits of paper to make paper snowflakes? Benjamin has discovered this pleasure & is obsessed! This is first thing this morning in our bed, leaving a little trail of tiny bits of paper everywhere. 
...
I’ve written a new blog post, not about paper snowflakes, or bits of paper everywhere, but about bits of myself, my mind & body scattered about. How #grief can effect your #mentalhealth, but how grief isn’t a #mentalillness. 
...
I wanted to share a bit more about my #anxiety and #fear after Luna died, what form it took & what I did that helped me. I guess I’m hoping there may be something in there for someone else who may themselves be in the grips of grief & feeling that they are scattered about all over the place.
...
I’m worried for all those mothers & families that have experienced the death of their baby during #COVID-19, that they may be falling through the cracks. I had a lot of help, but even back then, I had to seek most of it out myself. Even the choice of seeing the hospital #bereavementmidwife was optional. Turned out to be the best & first act of #selfcare I could have done, thank goodness she was brilliant. Sadly, I know this isn’t always the case.
...
There’s lots of things I’ve done to look after myself & ease my anxiety, but the most important two have been time & naming my feelings. In fact, just telling someone who is capable of holding safe space can be enough to make everything much more manageable. #dontsufferinsilence if you do one thing, find that trusted someone you can tell how you are really feeling. 
...
You can read more about what happened to me & what I did over in the link to my blog on my bio page. 
...
As always, thanks for reading and take gentle care. ❤️🙏🌙

shortcode_media.title: ¿Cómo sobrellevar un duelo cuando no pudiste despedir a tu ser querido?

node.text:
Durante la cuarentena vivimos  uno de los momentos más duros que un ser humano pudo pasar, muchos perdimos seres queridos, familiares muy cercanos, papá, mamá, hermano, hermana, esposo, esposa, etc... y que difícil es aceptar que partieron sin poderles dar una cristiana sepultura como corresponde, que triste es saber que ni siquiera podíamos ir a despedirnos de ellos y que simplemente teníamos que resignarnos a su partida sin un adiós. 

Fueron muchas las imágenes y videos que se mostraron de Guayaquil y que internacionalmente fuimos un ejemplo de lo que no se debió hacer...imágenes desgarradoras que no son fácil superar y que ahora la estan viviendo en otros países.

Sin dudar todos estos hechos ocurridos crearon traumas en muchas personas, es por esto que la @dra.mariavalcourt nos explica cómo debemos enfrentar esos traumas y como debemos manejar nuestro duelo.

«Siempre agradecidas por cada consejo y aporte valioso para poder enfrentar miedos, traumas, tristezas y saber que después de todo existen maneras de canalizarlos»

shortcode_media.accessibility_caption: Photo by YourLawyerFriend on August 29, 2020. Image may contain: one or more people, text that says 'JEE NEET EXAMS MINISTERS FROM 6 OPPOSITION- RULED STATES MOVE SUPREME COURT SEEKING REVIEW OF DECISION TO ALLOW NEET, JEE.'.

node.text:
Ministers from 6 Opposition-ruled States have moved the Apex Court seeking a review of its Aug 17 order, in which the Central Gov was permitted to conduct the National Eligibility cum Entrance Test (NEET) & Joint Entrance Examination (JEE) in Sept 2020.

The plea has been moved by Ministers from West Bengal, Jharkhand, Rajasthan, Chhattisgarh, Punjab & Maharashtra through Advocate Sunil Fernandes.

While the main petitioner is West Bengal Labour Minister Moloy Ghatak, other petitioners include Jharkhand Finance Minister Dr Rameshwar Oraon, Rajasthan Health Minister Dr Raghu Sharma, Chhattisgarh Planning Minister Amarjeet Bhagat, Punjab Heath Minister Balbir Singh Sidhu & Maharashtra Higher & Technical Education Minister Uday Ravindra Samant.

Several parties had opposed holding the NEET and JEE exams amid the ongoing COVID-19 pandemic & consulted on approaching the Supreme Court against its verdict. Notably, several protests were also held against conducting the exams.

West Bengal CM Mamata Banerjee had earlier this week said that opposition ruled states such as Maharashtra, Punjab, West Bengal, Jharkhand should collectively approach the SC for deferring NEET, JEE Main exams to be held next month.

node.text:
PEKANBARUINFO.COM, PEKANBARU-Kepala Dinas Komunikasi Informatika dan Statistik (Diskominfotik) Provinsi Riau, Chairul Riski memberikan keterangan terkait Surat Edaran (SE) Gubernur nomor 232/SE/2020, tentang Standar Operasional Prosedur Sistem Kerja Pada Masa Adaptasi Kebiasaan Baru di Lingkungan Pemerintah Provinsi Riau.

"Dengan surat edaran nomor 232/SE/2020 ini diharapkan pegawai di lingkungan pemerintah provinsi Riau dapat menyelesaikan dan mengikuti SOP yang saat masa adaptasi kebiasaan baru," katanya.

Menurutnya, Surat edaran ini menindaklanjuti surat edaran Gubernur nomor  171/SE/2020 tentang sistem kerja Pegawai Negeri Sipil (PNS) dan non PNS dalam tatanan normal baru di lingkungan pemerintah provinsi Riau.

Terangnya, Surat Edaran Gubernur Riau nomor 232/SE/2020 menjelaskan peran kepala perangkat daerah di lingkungan pemerintah provinsi Riau, apabila terdapat PNS dan non PNS terkonfirmasi Covid 19.

"Diantaranya seperti pertama, melakukan swab terlebih dahulu dilingkungan bidang atau bagian terhadap PNS atau non PNS yang terkonfirmasi positif covid 19," lanjutnya.

Gubernur Sumbar Sisipkan Aturan LGBT dalam Perda Ketahanan Keluarga
Kedua, jika ditemukan lebih dari satu bidang atau bagian PNS dan non PNS yang terkonfirmasi positif Covid 19 maka akan dilakukan swab secara keseluruhan. Ketiga, jika  terdapat PNS dan non PNS yang terkonfirmasi positif Covid 19 maka penyesuaian sistem kerja seperti work for home  atau work form office diatur oleh kepala perangkat daerah secara akuntabel, selektif dan proporsional serta dilaksanakan hingga hasil swab dikeluarkan oleh yang berwenang.

"Selanjutnya, kepala perangkat daerah melakukan evaluasi efektivitas proses kerja pegawai baik yang bekerja dari rumah maupun dikantor dan dilaporkan kepada Gubernur melalui Badan Kepegawaian Daerah Provinsi Riau," ucapnya.

Lebih lanjut, kelima, kepala perangkat daerah memastikan agar pegawai yang bekerja dari rumah maupun dikantor tidak mengganggu kelancaran penyelenggaraan pemerintah dan pelayanan publik.
Selengkapnya di www.pekanbaruinfo.com

ERC, Rally di Ungheria 2020: la seconda edizione del Rally di Ungheria rischia di saltare? 🤔 Secondo noi si, perché l'Ungheria dal 1° settembre chiuderà le frontiere a causa del Covid-19. 
Gergely Gulyas, vice premier del Governo Ungherese, ha affermato che nessun cittadino straniero potrà entrare in Ungheria dal 1° settembre, salvo qualche eccezione ancora da precisare. Per il Governo Ungherese tutti i paesi stranieri sono zona rossa. 
Il Governo Ungherese intanto sta trattando con la Uefa per organizzare al meglio la finale della Supercoppa fra il Bayer Monaco e il Siviglia. 
In questa manifestazione calcistica, che si terrà il 24 settembre, verrà riammesso nuovamente il pubblico (20 mila spettatori massimi su 68 mila posti). 
Ricordiamo che il rally ungherese si terrà dal 6 all'8 novembre... Per ora.

Sauna to ciepło, ale to nie to... Może sauna IR?⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
💖Więc jeśli macie jakieś sprawdzone metody na nasłonecznienie i poprawę humoru, to ja bardzo chętnie się dowiem...⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

Pięknego weekendu, ja mam jednak nadzieję, że może choć odrobinka chmur się rozejdzie...⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

Hydra Pro Waterproof Cart Bag

The Ben Sayers Hydra Pro Waterproof Cart Bag features an 8.5” top cuff with a 14-way graphite-friendly divider system.
The bags are made from a polyester-based waterproof fabric and feature thermo-sealed pocket seams to ensure that your equipment remains dry.
The stylish designs and bold colours ensure that the Hydra Pro range is both practical and looks great.
The ergonomic shoulder strap and hip pad are also fully waterproof and grab handles at the top and bottom of the bag ensure that this bag is incredibly easy and comfortable to carry and transport.
The bag includes nine thermo-sealed pockets to ensure that all of your clothing and equipment remains dry despite the weather. These pockets include a velour-lined valuables pocket, an insulated cooler pocket and two full-length clothing pockets.
The bag is fitted with a non-slip base for secure trolley use.
Additional features include an umbrella cord, towel carabiner, Velcro glove holder and detachable rain hood.

node.text:
Los Angeles: American actor, Chadwick Boseman who wan popularly known for his film, ‘Black Panther’ passed away in Los Angeles on Friday, August 28 after battling with colon cancer for almost 4 years. He was 43.

This news was confirmed by the late actor’s family in an official statement that was released on social media.

The statement read: ‘It is with immeasurable grief that we confirm the passing of Chadwick Boseman. Chadwick was diagnosed with stage III colon cancer in 2016 and battled with it these last 4 years as it progressed to stage IV. A true fighter, Chadwick persevered through it all, and brought you many of the films you have come to love so much.”
. 
. 
.

node.text:
Представительница команды Казахстана по тяжелой атлетике Зульфия Чиншанло заняла второе место на международном Кубке по тяжелой атлетике. Кубок является первым турниром в режиме онлайн.

Чиншанло выступила в категории до 55 килограммов. В сумме двоеборья она подняла 200 (85+115) килограммов.

Первое место осталось за Муаттар Набиевой из Узбекистан - 205 (95+110) килограммов.

Замкнула тройку лучших Йонна Лочовска из Польши - 185 (80+105) килограммов.

Зульфия Чиншанло - казахстанская тяжелоатлетка, трёхкратная чемпионка мира, которая установила несколько мировых рекордов. В возрасте 14 лет Зульфия была приглашена в Казахстан, заниматься тяжёлой атлетикой и уже через год вошла в сборную страны.

Также в  2009 году на чемпионате мира среди взрослых, в возрасте 16 лет Зульфия стала самым молодым чемпионом мира, побив предыдущий рекорд Ильи Ильина ставшего чемпионом мира в возрасте 17 лет.
